{"tid":2335863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"法國呢個世界上真係好多懶係嘢嘅人","createTime":"2020-12-22T07:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T09:15:43.000Z","uid":369713,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"691efefbdf5c8685ba308b77d7d4c8d0c0324449","tid":2335863,"uid":369713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺依家啲00後好xxxx?<br />\n覺唔覺以前xxx好好多？<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解咁鍾意一竹竿打沉一船人<br />\n然後夾硬將啲嘢用性別/年紀/年代/國籍分類再做總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最常見就係話港女乜乜乜、90後/00後乜乜乜、以前啲明星/歌/電視/電影好過依家好多<br />\n勁老屎忽心態 有時候啲人開呢啲topic嘅時候根本就冇了解過件事 就以單一嘅個別例子做總結<br />\n想營造眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2092a00bd02750712fd286e1a8edcc3352c002a8","tid":2335863,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬中回力鏢<br />\n此post 已完"},{"pid":"5480487cb39a2682bbbf6131a99c730c3d263269","tid":2335863,"uid":369713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2092a00bd02750712fd286e1a8edcc3352c002a8","tid":2335863,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬中回力鏢<br />\n此post 已完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"邊到中？佢哋係夾硬將人分類再標籤<br />\n我只係指出我見到嘅現象"},{"pid":"7125782c48254bcaf68fc0615d9b153244861580","tid":2335863,"uid":66365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5480487cb39a2682bbbf6131a99c730c3d263269","tid":2335863,"uid":369713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2092a00bd02750712fd286e1a8edcc3352c002a8","tid":2335863,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬中回力鏢<br />\n此post 已完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"邊到中？佢哋係夾硬將人分類再標籤<br />\n我只係指出我見到嘅現象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"一竹竿打晒成個法國既人，又用國籍黎分"},{